{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":668,"text":"At every stage of our lives"},{"time":2618,"text":"we make decisions that will profoundly influence"},{"time":6186,"text":"the lives of the people we're going to become,"},{"time":8072,"text":"and then when we become those people,"},{"time":9692,"text":"we're not always thrilled with the decisions we made."},{"time":12110,"text":"So young people pay good money"},{"time":14624,"text":"to get tattoos removed that teenagers"},{"time":17328,"text":"paid good money to get."},{"time":18698,"text":"Middle-aged people rushed to divorce people"},{"time":21206,"text":"who young adults rushed to marry."},{"time":23823,"text":"Older adults work hard to lose"},{"time":26460,"text":"what middle-aged adults worked hard to gain."},{"time":29160,"text":"On and on and on."},{"time":30276,"text":"The question is, as a psychologist,\nthat fascinates me is,"},{"time":33308,"text":"why do we make decisions"},{"time":35060,"text":"that our future selves so often regret?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38756,"text":"Now, I think one of the reasons --"},{"time":40608,"text":"I'll try to convince you today â€”"},{"time":42060,"text":"is that we have a fundamental misconception"},{"time":44620,"text":"about the power of time."},{"time":47452,"text":"Every one of you knows that the rate of change"},{"time":49932,"text":"slows over the human lifespan,"},{"time":51854,"text":"that your children seem to change by the minute"},{"time":54712,"text":"but your parents seem to change by the year."},{"time":57466,"text":"But what is the name of this magical point in life"},{"time":60886,"text":"where change suddenly goes"},{"time":62922,"text":"from a gallop to a crawl?"},{"time":64704,"text":"Is it teenage years? Is it middle age?"},{"time":67440,"text":"Is it old age? The answer, it turns out,"},{"time":70110,"text":"for most people, is now,"},{"time":72640,"text":"wherever now happens to be."},{"time":75591,"text":"What I want to convince you today"},{"time":77593,"text":"is that all of us are walking around with an illusion,"},{"time":80612,"text":"an illusion that history, our personal history,"},{"time":83830,"text":"has just come to an end,"},{"time":85444,"text":"that we have just recently become"},{"time":87051,"text":"the people that we were always meant to be"},{"time":90206,"text":"and will be for the rest of our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92652,"text":"Let me give you some data to back up that claim."},{"time":94756,"text":"So here's a study of change in people's"},{"time":97910,"text":"personal values over time."},{"time":99942,"text":"Here's three values."},{"time":101141,"text":"Everybody here holds all of them,"},{"time":102656,"text":"but you probably know that as you grow,"},{"time":104814,"text":"as you age, the balance of these values shifts."},{"time":108173,"text":"So how does it do so?"},{"time":110082,"text":"Well, we asked thousands of people."},{"time":112090,"text":"We asked half of them to predict for us"},{"time":113877,"text":"how much their values would\nchange in the next 10 years,"},{"time":116887,"text":"and the others to tell us"},{"time":118263,"text":"how much their values had\nchanged in the last 10 years."},{"time":121513,"text":"And this enabled us to do a really\ninteresting kind of analysis,"},{"time":124980,"text":"because it allowed us to compare the predictions"},{"time":127191,"text":"of people, say, 18 years old,"},{"time":129185,"text":"to the reports of people who were 28,"},{"time":131297,"text":"and to do that kind of analysis\nthroughout the lifespan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133917,"text":"Here's what we found."},{"time":135248,"text":"First of all, you are right,"},{"time":136541,"text":"change does slow down as we age,"},{"time":139389,"text":"but second, you're wrong,"},{"time":141281,"text":"because it doesn't slow nearly as much as we think."},{"time":144679,"text":"At every age, from 18 to 68 in our data set,"},{"time":148542,"text":"people vastly underestimated how much change"},{"time":152252,"text":"they would experience over the next 10 years."},{"time":155171,"text":"We call this the \"end of history\" illusion."},{"time":158105,"text":"To give you an idea of the magnitude of this effect,"},{"time":160488,"text":"you can connect these two lines,"},{"time":161710,"text":"and what you see here is that 18-year-olds"},{"time":164474,"text":"anticipate changing only as much"},{"time":166943,"text":"as 50-year-olds actually do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169928,"text":"Now it's not just values. It's all sorts of other things."},{"time":173482,"text":"For example, personality."},{"time":175300,"text":"Many of you know that psychologists now claim"},{"time":177966,"text":"that there are five fundamental\ndimensions of personality:"},{"time":181260,"text":"neuroticism, openness to experience,"},{"time":183527,"text":"agreeableness, extraversion, and conscientiousness."},{"time":187375,"text":"Again, we asked people how much they expected"},{"time":189622,"text":"to change over the next 10 years,"},{"time":191198,"text":"and also how much they had\nchanged over the last 10 years,"},{"time":194559,"text":"and what we found,"},{"time":195475,"text":"well, you're going to get used to\nseeing this diagram over and over,"},{"time":198030,"text":"because once again the rate of change"},{"time":200069,"text":"does slow as we age,"},{"time":201679,"text":"but at every age, people underestimate"},{"time":205567,"text":"how much their personalities will change"},{"time":207900,"text":"in the next decade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":209684,"text":"And it isn't just ephemeral things"},{"time":212005,"text":"like values and personality."},{"time":213859,"text":"You can ask people about their likes and dislikes,"},{"time":216874,"text":"their basic preferences."},{"time":218328,"text":"For example, name your best friend,"},{"time":221130,"text":"your favorite kind of vacation,"},{"time":222546,"text":"what's your favorite hobby,"},{"time":224312,"text":"what's your favorite kind of music."},{"time":226123,"text":"People can name these things."},{"time":227560,"text":"We ask half of them to tell us,"},{"time":229920,"text":"\"Do you think that that will\nchange over the next 10 years?\""},{"time":233313,"text":"and half of them to tell us,"},{"time":234467,"text":"\"Did that change over the last 10 years?\""},{"time":237158,"text":"And what we find, well, you've seen it twice now,"},{"time":239741,"text":"and here it is again:"},{"time":241583,"text":"people predict that the friend they have now"},{"time":244663,"text":"is the friend they'll have in 10 years,"},{"time":246211,"text":"the vacation they most enjoy now is the one"},{"time":248316,"text":"they'll enjoy in 10 years,"},{"time":249648,"text":"and yet, people who are 10 years older all say,"},{"time":252390,"text":"\"Eh, you know, that's really changed.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":255319,"text":"Does any of this matter?"},{"time":256475,"text":"Is this just a form of mis-prediction\nthat doesn't have consequences?"},{"time":259635,"text":"No, it matters quite a bit, and\nI'll give you an example of why."},{"time":262557,"text":"It bedevils our decision-making in important ways."},{"time":266022,"text":"Bring to mind right now for yourself"},{"time":267727,"text":"your favorite musician today"},{"time":270000,"text":"and your favorite musician 10 years ago."},{"time":272368,"text":"I put mine up on the screen to help you along."},{"time":274927,"text":"Now we asked people"},{"time":276530,"text":"to predict for us, to tell us"},{"time":278767,"text":"how much money they would pay right now"},{"time":281654,"text":"to see their current favorite musician"},{"time":283990,"text":"perform in concert 10 years from now,"},{"time":286507,"text":"and on average, people said they would pay"},{"time":288554,"text":"129 dollars for that ticket."},{"time":291271,"text":"And yet, when we asked them\nhow much they would pay"},{"time":294198,"text":"to see the person who was their favorite"},{"time":296519,"text":"10 years ago perform today,"},{"time":298558,"text":"they say only 80 dollars."},{"time":300400,"text":"Now, in a perfectly rational world,"},{"time":302238,"text":"these should be the same number,"},{"time":304352,"text":"but we overpay for the opportunity"},{"time":306863,"text":"to indulge our current preferences"},{"time":308966,"text":"because we overestimate their stability."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312286,"text":"Why does this happen? We're not entirely sure,"},{"time":314734,"text":"but it probably has to do"},{"time":316280,"text":"with the ease of remembering"},{"time":318459,"text":"versus the difficulty of imagining."},{"time":320980,"text":"Most of us can remember\nwho we were 10 years ago,"},{"time":323449,"text":"but we find it hard to imagine who we're going to be,"},{"time":326188,"text":"and then we mistakenly think\nthat because it's hard to imagine,"},{"time":329193,"text":"it's not likely to happen."},{"time":331267,"text":"Sorry, when people say \"I can't imagine that,\""},{"time":334522,"text":"they're usually talking about\ntheir own lack of imagination,"},{"time":337470,"text":"and not about the unlikelihood"},{"time":338962,"text":"of the event that they're describing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341952,"text":"The bottom line is, time is a powerful force."},{"time":345519,"text":"It transforms our preferences."},{"time":347162,"text":"It reshapes our values."},{"time":349280,"text":"It alters our personalities."},{"time":350623,"text":"We seem to appreciate this fact,"},{"time":353190,"text":"but only in retrospect."},{"time":354751,"text":"Only when we look backwards do we realize"},{"time":357246,"text":"how much change happens in a decade."},{"time":360518,"text":"It's as if, for most of us,"},{"time":362197,"text":"the present is a magic time."},{"time":364366,"text":"It's a watershed on the timeline."},{"time":366383,"text":"It's the moment at which we finally"},{"time":368727,"text":"become ourselves."},{"time":371230,"text":"Human beings are works in progress"},{"time":373923,"text":"that mistakenly think they're finished."},{"time":376846,"text":"The person you are right now"},{"time":378636,"text":"is as transient, as fleeting and as temporary"},{"time":382338,"text":"as all the people you've ever been."},{"time":384997,"text":"The one constant in our life is change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388545,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390641,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}